<br>
Also have Earthen Boots hwen you can to kill pets gone wrong.<br>
<br>
learn to get your BACK to a wall or corner so you can channel spells through any damage (but not bashes) (thats a BIG hubba hubba thing to know, a lot of folk have died ebcause they didnt know)<br>
<br>
AOE spells rock, the poitn blank ones with fast cast times, there's a few levels though the PB AOEs we get arent up to dealing with mobs so beware of that.<br>
<br>
Runners suck you have to learn to nuke mobs as they get to that RUN stage of health.<br>
<br>
Study zones invisible to get an idea of them.<br>
<br>
get a SOW up before ocming in if possible.<br>
<br>
Sow and heal potions RULE,well worth cash ic can afford (heal potions needs ice giant toes and balm leaves if I remember right 40+pp per shot INSTA heals 300 hp)<br>
<br>
get your defence offence skills up, take hits, regen with phantom spells or bandaids, it's vital to get ac/dodge up to help with hits. You will often have to take mobs down with melee, even at high lvl (*hugs chardok dagger*)<br>
<br>
learn to chain cast pets (its hard but rules)<br>
<br>
HP AC mana gear is vital.<br>
<br>
Redorious<br>
Archmage<br>
karana<br>
