<br>
I was fooling around in Tower of Frozen Shadow last night and I used my Clay Braclet (check www.magecompendium.com link at the bottom of this page) for free Eyes to go scout ahead and pick out the wandering mobs and time when to kill them away from static spawns.<br>
<br>
When scouting ALWAYS ALWAYS ALWAYS have up see invis and levitate to avoid pit traps. If you scout with Eye of Zomm be aware that it will fall into the traps (which can be a good thing).<br>
<br>
And last, if you don't mind spoiler info, check out <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.eqatlas.com"></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> for maps and then link to Alakazams site from the EQAtlas maps for other zone info.<br>
